By Ethan Hunts Let’s just clear something up real-quick. Bill Gates doesn’t act poor. This car was limited to 300 copies. And for a time – banned in the US — Due to vehicle safety restrictions. With a lawyer, he managed to have the legislation changed and imported the car. Want to know more about Bill Gates? Here’s a snippet of an infographic-timeline I built of his life here. In conclusion, just because Gates doesn’t spew out money like a peacock, doesn’t mean he lives like a poor man. Source: Quora